https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500null Behind the scenes documentary about the making of Macbeth 3000: This time, it's personal. The cast and crew share the story of how a group of teenagers from suburban Canada were able to produce a full length action-comedy Shakespeare/James Bond hybrid to life, up to the world premiere in at Toronto's Bloor Cinema in 2005.
